tch Lu and he was found not guilty. Prosecutors said they would not appeal.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2015/12/31/2003636098|title=Man found not guilty of 2000 murder of girlfriend after new DNA evidence|last=Pan|first=Jason|date=2015-12-31|website=Taipei Times|publisher=|access-date=30 September 2017}}</ref> |}
